                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-521" type="given" value="ANNE"></interp>ANNE BAIGENT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my parents. I was in Aldgate that day, and saw the prisoner run and put something into his pocket—he ran towards the Minories, and I lost sight of him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440506-name-522" type="witnessName">
