                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-522" type="given" value="MICHAEL"></interp>MICHAEL CONDEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 138.) I was coming up the Mino<lb></lb>ries, and saw a mob round the prosecutrix—I went to her, and from her description I went to the prisoner's house, in Gower's-walk, Whitechapel about half an hour afterwards, I found him with two others—he was in the act of shifting his clothes—he was taking his coat off—he sometimes goes out in a jacket—I would not let him put on another coat.</p>
               <p>
